      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELSA ABOVE (2) is a classy pup building a strong winning record at the journey. Has been on speed to score at her last couple of runs. Scored latest at Dubbo in a handy 23.07. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Hard to go past. FROM THE DISCO (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Shorty (25.11) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Leading chance. ELLA KNOWS (5) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Kalani Sea (25.38) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can measure up. MOTOR CITY MINI (4) warrants respect following a recent placing.",
